There won’t be much room at the new Premier Inn, but then that’s the idea

The first Hub will open on St Martin’s Lane in central London next summer
Premier Inn
  • A Hub room by Premier Inn
    1 of 1
    The first Hub will open on St Martin’s Lane in central London next summer Premier Inn

Its bedrooms will be small and room rates will be cheap, but Whitbread claims that its low-cost Hub by Premier Inn brand will offer cutting-edge technology — and a decent shower and comfy bed.

A smartphone app will enable guests to book and check-in online, pre-set the room temperature and light settings and even choose which television or radio channel they want playing in their room when they arrive.
